Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Zeref really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even move...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Zeref really said Acnologia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation of Tenroujima \Nis over and done with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rattle, rattle... Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Laxus showed up and \Nall... It fits the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you cut that out since \NLily is scared of thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crakabadaboom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in honor of Natsu turning \Ninto a Thunder-Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really all we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how important our mission is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a responsibility \Nto protect my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, I have \Nno choice but to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leaving them there? When there are \Nlives that could possibly be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like that, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you compare it to maintaining the \Norder and justice of the entire Magical World...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call this justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:03.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to argue with what I call \Njustice and ideals, Dranbalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that will satisfy you, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Deepest Realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:20.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your characters will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I lazily wrote runes \Njust to protect my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wrote runes like this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I did it so you wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you don't know \Nthe character for "to learn"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes! Your characters will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your crappy roundabout runes seem infantile
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:58.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,before my single characters \Nand their countless meanings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:57.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is quite hard on the ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My runes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:03.84,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble becomes resound!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the character means more \Nthan just sound, it means expanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he uses characters to strengthen \Nthe effects of his characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:20.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's simple, but it has deep meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you have not realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The line that connects two points...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the things called "words"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roundabout...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have they been going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Theory vs. Theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that arguing over pointless things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Baryon Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Egg Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautifully fried-peron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to cook {\i1}you{\i0} next-peron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's having a \Nrough time over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to join in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle we just had \Nused up all our magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be out of strength \Nand magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's food right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Elf-niichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarin' to go, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Maybe it's only temporary, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fusion of flame and lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thunder-Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as when he ate Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:39.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After hitting him with flames, he \Nfollowed up with a lightning attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Egg Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.21,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself, Elfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:56.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can barely stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Even if I don't have enough \Nmagic power for a full body Take-Over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have this arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have hurt my little sister \NLisanna, and made my older sister cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This helpless arm couldn't \Neven protect my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Elfman, the Man, will put everything he's got \Ninto this arm as a Fairy Tail wizard and beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:27.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three as one! You'll fill in for Ever's role!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up with the "Man, Man" stuff-pero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaningless words hold no power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ecriture of Darkness! Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:37.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, my babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it hurt so much-pero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your claws are dull!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need is yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:10.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad timing for an impromptu \Ncombination, Elfman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just see something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:23.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky we didn't draw him \Nfor the first test...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we managed to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally drained...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think maybe now I'll rest a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt our guild, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't use your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:30.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Thunder-Flame Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really outta magic power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With such overwhelming magic power, it \Nlooks like he consumed it just as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world is the power source?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:32.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With a ship this big, it should \Nbe powered by a huge lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are we crawling through this passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me, ask Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A hunch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't just stop all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just bumped, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:59.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Carla bumped my butt, then \Nthat means you bumped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for stopping so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just bumped into Carla's \Nbutt with a *pomf*...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, isn't that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually complaining about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, we're having a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, more importantly... \NWhat caught your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such impressive youths...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov, you bastard... You've raised \Nsome fearsome whippersnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many decades has it been since \Nsomeone has beaten me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a trivial matter to clean up now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:23.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I must honor you properly for \Nshowing me an enjoyable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that attack didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:33.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's Eye... Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you all, special...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a realm which far \Nsurpasses even your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt magic power like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:06.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is over, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:15.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have enough strength to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like a power source exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart... Devil's Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear voices inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! How did they get in the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been found!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:41.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold off the enemy! \NYou two, stop that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the tiny cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:50.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stomp him flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You've done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, sure... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like all we can do \Nis try fiddling with stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword that can change size?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like my sword, the Buster Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's one thing we'll \Nprotect, it's this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! I will make this my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... My Musica Sword... That was expensive! {This is a Rave Master reference and the official spelling in english is "Musica"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll turn you into fish food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... feel like my mind \Nis floating far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What indescribable magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, get yourself together! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The farther along the \Npath of magic you tread,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the deeper you sink toward \Nthe depths of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what you find there in \Nthe depths, glistening...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the One Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:11.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little farther... Just a little \Nfarther and I will reach the One Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that "just a little" is so very deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To fill that depth, the World \Nof Great Magic is needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A world with Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:30.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the world will change \Nwith Zeref's awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, it will finally come into my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:44.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I've heard \Nthis somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all cannot go to the \NWorld of Great Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:55.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You lack the conviction \Nto dive into the depths!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of pose is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Book of Zeref, Volume 4, \NVerse 20: Hidden Magic, Nemesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He made monsters from the rubble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the magic power from the deepest depths,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:33.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you can even create devils \Nfrom lumps of earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make the devils do your \Nbidding, as heaven's judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Hidden Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:45.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One after another... Every spell \Na bundle of magical despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:57.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared... I'm scared... I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... shaking in fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, give us the courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:33.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I've got my friends this close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear is not evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:40.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It tells you what your weakness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:46.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you know your weakness, you \Ncan become stronger as well as kinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know our weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what'll we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stand up and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can't help being scared alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're all right here, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:23.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got our friends close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your vanity is praiseworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that ends now, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as our friends are with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't have any magic power left...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we won't give up until the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do without any magic power left?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance, Dirt Devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Send everything to the pits of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail, your sun has set!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, it's the last spurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll make 'em pay for \Npicking a fight with Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! And you have a plan for that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plan? I've got the same plan I always have!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:11.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! My plan is, of course, CHARGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dawn on Tenroujima
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:20.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I'm the Salamander, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to kill the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.72,0:24:24.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my bad.
